{
  "text": "In recent years, en bloc resection with ESD in large lesions have become attractive in the management of patients with BE neoplasia [CITATION_1] [CITATION_2] [CITATION_3] . ESD is only available in expert centres with highly skilled operators. The use of the EMR Captivator device in BE neoplasia can potentially mimic this for larger lesions by acquiring larger tissue specimens and therefore in comparison to the Duette device, it may become the preferred tool for larger lesions.",
  "correct_citation": {
